ass="section-content"><div class="section-header"><div class="section-header__title-container"><h2 class="section-header__title">Services</h2><div class="section-header__bg-title">SIDEKICKS</div></div><h4 class="section-header__subtitle">Enhancing Your Travel Experience with Indian Comforts</h4></div><div class="services-section__container"><div class="feature-card feature-card--img-top-left " style="grid-area:card1"><div class="floating-icon floating-icon--below"><img src="/images/services/plane.png" alt="" draggable="false"/></div><div class="feature-card__number">1</div><div class="feature-card__content">Personalized airport transfers and seamless arrival assistance</div></div><div class="feature-card feature-card--img-left-center " style="grid-area:card2"><div class="floating-icon floating-icon--above"><img src="/images/services/people.png" alt="" draggable="false"/></div><div class="feature-card__number">2</div><div class="feature-card__content">Private and small-group sightseeing tours infused with Indian cultural insights</div></div><div class="feature-card feature-card--img-bottom-left " style="grid-area:card3"><div class="floating-icon floating-icon--above"><img src="/images/services/cab.png" alt="" draggable="false"/></div><div class="feature-card__number">3</div><div class="feature-card__content">Indian-operated vehicles and on-ground handling for maximum comfort</div></div><img class="services-section__container--image" style="grid-area:image" src="/images/services/services.jpg" alt="Services Cover Image"/><div class="feature-card feature-card--img-top-center " style="grid-area:card4"><div class="floating-icon floating-icon--below"><img src="/images/services/cutlery.png" alt="" draggable="false"/></div><div class="feature-card__number">4</div><div class="feature-card__content">Guaranteed access to authentic Indian meals during your travels</div></div><div class="feature-card feature-card--img-right-center " style="grid-area:card5"><div class="floating-icon floating-icon--below"><img src="/images/services/manager.png" alt="" draggable="false"/></div><div class="feature-card__number">5</div><div class="feature-card__content">Multilingual Indian tour managers ensuring smooth communication</div></div><div class="feature-card feature-card--img-bottom-right " style="grid-area:card6"><div class="floating-icon floating-icon--below"><img src="/images/services/support.png" alt="" draggable="false"/></div><div class="feature-card__number">6</div><div class="feature-card__content">Premium luxury travel with dedicated customer support</div></div></div></div></section><section id="contact" class="contact-section section"><img class="contact-section__bg" src="/images/contact.jpg" alt="Services Cover Image"/><div class="section-content"><div class="section-content__header-container"><div class="section-header"><div class="section-header__title-container"><h2 class="section-header__title" style="text-align:left;color:#fff">Book Your Holidays Today!</h2></div><h4 class="section-header__subtitle" style="text-align:left;color:#fff">Begin your dream journey with India’s top South &amp; Latin America travel experts.</h4></div></div><form class="contact-form"><div class="contact-form__group"><label class="contact-form__label">Are you an agent?</label><div class="contact-form__radio-group "><label><input type="radio" name="userType"/>Yes</label><label><input type="radio" name="userType" checked=""/>No</label></div></div><div class="contact-form__row" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr)"><div class="contact-form__group"><div class="textfield"><label class="textfield__label">Full Name<!-- --> <!-- -->*</label><div class="textfield__wrapper"><input type="text" placeholder="Enter your full name" required="" class="textfield__input " validation="[object Object]" name="name" value=""/></div><div class="textfield__error"></div></div></div><div class="contact-form__group"><div class="textfield"><label class="textfield__label">Number of PAX<!-- --> <!-- -->*</label><div class="textfield__wrapper"><input type="number" placeholder="Enter number of attendees" required="" class="textfield__input " validation="[object Object]" name="pax" value=""/></div><div class="textfield__error"></div></div></div></div><div class="contact-form__row" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr)"><div class="contact-form__group"><div class="textfield"><label class="textfield__label">Mobile Number<!-- --> <!-- -->*</label><div class="textfield__wrapper"><div class=" react-tel-input "><div class="special-label">Phone</div><input class="form-control textfield__input textfield__input--phone" placeholder="0000000000" type="tel" required="" name="mobile" value="+91"/><div class="flag-dropdown textfield__phone-btn"><div class="selected-flag" title="India: + 91" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-haspopup="listbox"><div class="flag in"><div class="arrow"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="textfield__error"></div></div></div><div class="contact-form__group"><div class="textfield"><label class="textfield__label">Email<!-- --> <!-- -->*</label><div class="textfield__wrapper"><input type="email" placeholder="Enter email address" required="" class="textfield__input " validation="[object Object]" name="email" value=""/></div><div class="textfield__error"></div></div></div></div><button class="er-btn " type="submit" disabled="" style="background-color:#000000">Submit</button></form></div></section><section id="faq" class="faq-section section"><div class="section-content"><div class="section-header" style="gap:1rem"><div class="section-header__title-container"><h2 class="section-header__title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2></div><h4 class="section-header__subtitle">Your Questions Answered: Everything You Need to Know About Our Tours</h4></div><div class="faq-list"><div class="faq-item "><div class="faq-question"><h3>Which countries do you cover?</h3><span class="faq-icon">+</span></div><div class="faq-answer" style="max-height:0px"><p>We offer customized tours in Brazil, Argentina, Peru, Colombia, Costa Rica, and Mexico, focused on Indian travelers.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item "><div class="faq-question"><h3>Are Indian meals available?</h3><span class="faq-icon">+</span></div><div class="faq-answer" style="max-height:0px"><p>Yes, we ensure access to authentic Indian cuisine at every major stop.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item "><div class="faq-question"><h3>Are the tours suitable for NRIs?</h3><span class="faq-icon">+</span></div><div class="faq-answer" style="max-height:0px"><p>Absolutely, we tailor the experience with cultural familiarity and language support for NRIs.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item "><div class="faq-question"><h3>What languages do the guides speak?</h3><span class="faq-icon">+</span></div><div class="faq-answer" style="max-height:0px"><p>Our Indian tour managers speak Hindi, English, Portuguese, and Spanish fluently.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="banner-section section"><div class="section-content"><img class="banner-section__image" src="/images/packages/five-countries-grand-south-america-2026/package13-La Paz.jpg" alt="Services Cover Image"/><div class="section-header" style="gap:1rem"><div class="section-header__title-container"><h2 class="section-header__title" style="color:#fff">Ready to get started?</h2></div><h4 class="section-header__subtitle" style="color:#fff;font-weight:200">Begin your dream journey with India’s top South &amp; Latin America travel experts.</h4></div><button class="er-btn " type="button" style="background-color:#fff;color:#000" link="/#contact">Contact Us</button></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--><footer class="footer section"><div class="section-content"><div class="footer__content"><div class="footer__col footer__col--1"><img src="/images/logo.jpg" alt="Brand Logo" class="footer__logo"/><p class="footer__text">Explore the best destinations with our expert-crafted travel experiences.</p><div cl